'''卡劳帕帕'''（{{lang-en|Kalaupapa, Hawaii}}）是[[美国|美国]][[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]][[卡拉沃县_(夏威夷州)|卡拉沃县]]的一个[[未建制社区|未建制社区]]，地处[[摩洛凯岛|摩洛凯岛]]北岸卡劳帕帕半岛底部，历史上曾是麻风病人的定居点，现已设立卡劳帕帕国家历史公园。其附近因有世界上最高的海岸悬崖（高1097米-1188米）而闻名于世<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 人民网 | title = 组图：全球十大最绚丽悬崖 小新之父失足悬崖在内 | url = http://travel.people.com.cn/GB/156051/10168642.html | date = 2009-10-10 | accessdate = 2011-11-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150613231913/http://travel.people.com.cn/GB/156051/10168642.html | archive-date = 2015-06-13 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gohawaii.com/cn/molokai/regions-neighborhoods/central-molokai/kalaupapa-national-historic-park |title=摩洛凯岛卡劳帕帕国家历史公园 |accessdate=2011-11-24 |archive-date=2011-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110911054657/http://www.gohawaii.com/cn/molokai/regions-neighborhoods/central-molokai/kalaupapa-national-historic-park |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

